Remote Acquisition Boot Environment (RABE): rabe-server_iso
===========================================================

This creates a basic RABE server installation ISO using the Ubuntu Server 14.04.1 LTS installation ISO.
It downloads this ISO from the Ubuntu website. If it is already available in the 'images/' directory, it will use that one instead.
One can also manually input an Ubuntu Server x86_64 installation ISO.
After executing, the RABE server installation ISO can be found in the 'images/' directory.

NAME
	make_rabe-server_iso

SYNOPSIS
	./make_rabe-server_iso [-f ISO file]

DESCRIPTION
	Create Remote Acquisition Boot Environment (RABE) server installation ISO.

	[-f ISO file]
		manual Ubuntu Server x86_64 installation ISO input